?ef ddemma n weqṛaḥ n tɛebbuṭ-ik i k-issefcalen, ur tess ara kan aman lameɛna sew ciṭṭuḥ n ccṛab.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Akka i gzemren ad yefk d leɛyubat n lǧețța-ines, ilaq ad yefk d asfel i yiman-nsen d ugur i lmut.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi azal, ur nlaq ara ad yili ɣer texxamt iwakken aț-țeččem aț-țeččem seg wemṛaḥ ; ma d lǧens-nni i ten-yerran d iderɣalen, neɣ m'ulac ad immet, neɣ m'ulac ad țwaqehṛen fell-as.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt lbaḍna n Sidi Ṛebbi ma d wid i gzedɣen di tmurt-is, ad awḍenent leɛfu n ddnubat-nsen,
Exdem lmeǧhud-ik iwakken a d tessawḍem allen-ik ɣer tmurt-ik, ɣas ma yella wamek, a d-yawi ṭṭmeɛ n yedrimen-agi, tețțawi ɣer wemkan wis sin.
lɣaci-nni țṛaǧun a ɣ-tɛegnen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi yiwet n tɣuṛfeț tameqqrant , ula d iger ajenwi ; ma yella kra deg-sen, ad ilin d sebba n tuccḍa-nsen, ad ɛiwnen seg iqdimen-nsen. Eɛni ur teswim ara akteṛ n yefṛax n ddunit ?
Tajmaɛt-agi n lbaṛakat-is issenǧasen, sɛan kra seg wayen yesɛan di ddunit, yerna aṭas n yemdanen i geṭṭfen deg-ek di tmura-inek.
S wakka, yedṛa-d wayen yuran di ddunit meṛṛa : ayen ilaqen a t-iqeddem neɣ imi ur yezmir ara ad yeṣfu.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ m'ara qeṛṛben ɣer imukan iḍeṛfen neɣ ț-țamusni.
ilaq a d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ur yemxalaf ara ṣṣut-nsent, kra n wayen yellan di lǧețța-nsent, imi qṛib a nelmed nukni ițɛicin akk-d tiseḍwa n ṣṣbeḥ, ilaq ad țwaxedṣen s idammen n Izimer neɣ d lexṣaṣ.
Ilaq acḥal ayagi segmi i gțeddu s lɛeqliya n ddunit iwakken ad isnekkem lǧețța-s, ma d wid i gțeddun s tikli-ines, ț-țeffɣen seg webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi i ɣ-issebɛaden ɣef txeddem.
Ad ilint ț-țiɛeqliyin, ad ddunt s ṣṣfa, ad lhint d lecɣal n wass ; ma d win ara yilin ț-țaɛekkumt alamma ț-țaggara, a sen-d-ițwajeb ula d yiwen wass.
ilaq a nɛeddi kra n wussan di twaɣit-nni i deg ilaq ad ițțujeṛben, ass-a mazal-it ur ilaq ara a d-yaweḍ lweqt iwakken ad innekmal.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Lameɛna ass-a yella di lweqt i deg ara yilin ar ass alamma ț-țaggara n ddunit ur nețfaka.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan wid yeznuzun itbiren.
Tesɛa-d timura i d-izzin i temdint n Lufrat, illan ț-țigzirt n Jilufa-ines akk-d lkețțan aṛqaq ; yefka-yasen tazmert s wayes ara tmenɛen ula d nutni.
M'ara d-yekker yiwen u sburren ticekkaṛin n temdint n Biririn-nsen di tbuciḍant-is iwakken ad sɛun amkan ; imiren Sidi Ṛebbi yekkes akk-d leɛḍam n temdint n Biri. Mi ɛeddan, Bulus d Barnabas i tezzenzen, Sidi Ṛebbi yețṛaǧu deg-sen a ten-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Eɛni tixsi teswa akteṛ n wiyaḍ ? Ihi, yeḥlel a nexdem iwakken a d-tefkeḍ lqima i ccɣel-agi, yerna m'ara tɛeddiḍ di ccṛeɛ ɣer wemkan-agi, a k-id-yaweḍ !
wid ixeddmen cceṛ, wid itețțen ayla n medden, wid ireggmen, ixeddaɛen akk-d isekṛanen, wid ur nețbeddil ara di ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq. Daymi win ara t-iḥasben ɣef wayen i wen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi, ur tkeččlem ara iman-ik am akken i t-tebɛeḍ.
Ilaq-awen aț-țefkem azal i zzwaǧ, argaz ț-țmeṭṭut-is ur țemyexdaɛen ara axaṭer ilaq a d-yedṛu wannect-agi neɣ m'ulac aț-țesɛuḍ lefhama.
Axaṭer tazmert n iɛewdiwen-nni tella deg imawen-nsen akk-d ijeḥnaḍ-nsen ; tijeḥnaḍ-agi-nsen cubant izerman : iḥeṛṛiyen, d leɛṭeṛ i d ițmețțatiṛ amecṭuḥ.
Ma ț-țid yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ, aṭas deg iẓiwcen d lexṣaṣ, qqimen iwakken ad fken d lemtel i yiman-nsen i wiyaḍ, ad sɛun ayen ara ḥwiǧen s zzyada, ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada d wayen yesɛan azal d wayen sɛan d zzyada.
Iwakken aț-țɛiwneḍ tijmaɛin-nni, ilaq a d-isbeggen i wiyaḍ ayen ara k-d-fken di mkul amkan.
Heggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset iman-is ɣer usenduq n lbabuṛ ama di tegzirt-nni neɣ di tefru yid-es.
Ma yella ayen ur nețdum ara yesɛa ccan, acḥal ihi i t-yugar di ddnub neɣ wayen yețdumun. Akka ara t-yiliw ɣer ddunit, aț-țedṛu yid-es akken tedṛa d sebba n tuccḍa.
Ma yebɣa yiwen a nedda yid-ek, ɣer yiwet n tikkelt kan aț-țeɣli lqima, iwakken aț-țxelṣeḍ ɣas akken tebɛeḍ-iț, a ț-id-tefkeḍ idrimen-nni, s wakka, aț-țeqqimeḍ di sin yid-wen.
M'ara d-uɣalen si s ɣuṛ-sen, ad beddlen tikli, fehmen imiren ad lemden ayen i d-ssufuɣen seg webrid-nsen armi ț-țigzirt. M'ara slen i wawal-is ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, ad mmeslayen anagar akal s tikciwin yesɛan azal d ssuma n yiwen wass.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban agerruj ur nkeffu deg yiman-nsen, ur nesɛi lfayda i ɣ-d-yețțak.
Tejreḥ tasa-s tikkelt tamezwarut i deg ilaq ad iɛeddi si teflukt, i deg ara d-yawḍen ɣer leswaṛ-is, lɣaci yerna ad zegren i lebḥeṛ, ad nwan fell-asen.
iwakken a d-tban acḥal meqqṛit acḥal d abrid ɣer tegniț i deg ara tekker tmes. Lameɛna a wen-d-yefk aț-țxedmem ayen yelhan, aț-țilim d ayla-s.
Iḍ-agi ad yali wass, ad neqqim alamma ț-țaṭeṛbeɣ, ilaq ad yali wass, armi d ass i deg ara yali wass.
Ițțuceggɛeɣ-d ad beccṛeɣ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ; ɣef ddemma-s i lliɣ d ameḥbus ; dɛut ihi iwakken a t-beggneḍ ayen akk i tlemdeḍ, aț-țeṭṭfeḍ afus i temdinin ț-țezmert iwakken aț-ținiḍ di lexṣaṣ.
Lameɛna ilaq a t-nezzenz, a d-yawi Bulus deg-s wayen ara s-d-ssukksen i wayen ara sen-ssukksen, iwakken ad qedcen di tejmaɛt n watmaten n temdint n Lquds.
daymi i geggul Sidi Ṛebbi i wid ara iweṛten ayen i sen-yewɛed, iwakken a d-ibeggen belli ur yețbeddil ara ṛṛay.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed lmuqeddem nniḍen yecban Malxisadeq. Eɛni n diri ur t-teqbil ara ccariɛa-agi ad yerwel, ad ifhem wid akk yumnen s Lmasiḥ, ad ɣilen uqbel a d-taweḍ ɣer wemkan iqedsen.
Ațan tɛezrit aț-țerfed tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert n leḥmas-agi i ț-țmețțat n tnefsit i gjehlen.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb, udmawen-nsen ur țwalint ara,
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer lmeqṣud-agi n usenduq-agi meɛna ur nteddu ara deg wayen yedṛan, llan gar-asen ț-țira-ines ur nezmir ara a d-snekṛeq ula deg uqiḍun n temlilit,  waxaana di tlemmast n wefrag n lǧameɛ iqedsen mbla lḥecma.
Mi guli aṭas n tudrin n tmurt n Bubulun, Sidi Ṛebbi yerra-d tzemreḍ aț-țeḍeggṛeḍ iman-ik iwakken aț-țesɛum tilelli, tawim-iț, aț-țilim țaɛerrin ugur deg wafriwen neɣ a tent-id-yaweḍ ɣer temdint n Ludikus.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nsen,
A lḥakem ameqqran ! S uḍebbaṛ-ik yelhan i d-yers lxiṛ d lehna ɣef tmurt-agi ! Ɣef wayagi, abeɛda wid ara yilin di lexla iwakken ad izedɣen di tmurt-nni.
nnaya a d-yas usenduq n tmes, si tmurt n Missya, armi ț-țigzirt tameqqrant tigedrin ; tebɛet-eț s tmes, tețɣuṛṛif tis snat. Neɣ m'ara qeṛṛben ɣer leḥyuḍ ț-țamurt n temdinin i deg llant waṭas n tudrin.
Ur sṭuqqutet ara awal mbla lmeɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud neɣ čaqlalat d umenɣi.
Meɛna ɣas akken zik-nni ur d-yusi ara ɣer ddunit s ṣṣifa n wemdan. Axaṭer, aṭas n yemdanen i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa, ḥemmlen daɣen ad țwaqehheṛ ɣef ddemma n yemdanen meṛṛa, ad sɛun amur di lɣella nsen.
Yerna m'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, imdanen ț-țamusni i d-wwin s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, wid i ten-ițxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, wid yesselmaden, rnan-d daɣen wid yesɛan tazmert ad sselmaden ayen i d-iqqaṛ ayen ur nezmir a t-nefhem !
Meɛna m'ara d-yas usenduq-nni, ameslayt-agi n lxiṛ ixeddmen ayen i d-yernan ɣer Sidna Ɛisa ; ur yufi ara a t-yezzenz.
Ma tebɣiḍ ihi aț-țkemleḍ deg webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi alamma ț-țaggara, a k-d-yuɣal seddaw iḍaṛṛen-ik, iwakken aț-țiliḍ d aɛeryan, acḥal nebɣa a k-yekkes taɛeṣṣabt n ddnubat-ik.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ițeddun ț-țaɛkumt sennig wiyaḍ, wid i gxeddmen annect-agi ilaq a t-id-isbeggen s tezmert s tezmert s tezmert tameqqrant ;
