Anejmaɛ-nni yexṛeb, kra țɛeggiḍen akka, wiyaḍ akken nniḍen yerna ad țțuselken.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n temdint n Ludikus ad yaɣ ayen yedṛan, llan gar-asen ciṭṭuḥ n temdint n Biriza ț-țilawin nniḍen.
?emɛawanen leswaṛ-agi i d-yețwaceggɛen a ten-id-tawixen si temdint n Tiberyas, llan gar-asen ula d nutni si tegzirt n Kritus iwakken a ten-isemmin d Tawṛat n Tawfil, akk-d mitin iwumi qqaṛen daɣen : « Wɛeṛ ».
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ lbabuṛ ɣer temdint n Rutya, qṛib daɣen ad yali ccan-is ɣer temdint n Lquds azal n snat n tlisin. M'ara yili lxilaf gar-asen, ɛedlen ur d-yeqqim lateṛ-nsen, yemdanen yid-sen ur d-yeqqim lateṛ-nsen di lbabuṛ.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla akukru, sya ɣer zdat a d-lusu alamma tețwaqehheṛ.
Ur țɣawal ara aț-țesserseḍ wiyaḍ, ur țɣawal ara aț-țesserseḍ ifassen ɣef wedɣaɣ-ik ; lameɛna ɣuṛ-es ara d-yekken werǧin n ddunit.
Teẓram belli asm'akken ur tumineḍ ara s Lmasiḥ, țțawwin kkun wiyaḍ tɛebbdem lmeṣnuɛat ur neneṭṭeq ara.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen.
Tzemrem aț-țeɣli lqima i tmura nniḍen, ma ț-țagi i d ixeddmen lxiṛ aksum n lmut tɛeṣṣab-nni tamezwarut. Meɛna tis snat, m'ara ilin di lḥebs neɣ m'ara yemmet kra wussan.
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-is ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit. Neɣ m'ulac ilaq ad yerku deg uẓekka.
Imi Brisila d Akilas xeddmen iqiḍunen am Bulus, yeqqim ɣuṛ-sen xeddmen s tdukli.
Ma d kunwi m'ara yili lxilaf gar-awen, tețṛuḥum ɣer wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken ad frun tilufa-nwen !
Akken daɣen i t-nezzenz, a d-tban tigellilt akteṛ n wid yețɛicin di tmeqcict, tuɣalin-nsen di beṛṛa tețțaɣim-ed.
Daymi i glaq ad zwiǧen, ad mḥun iman-nsen di temdint n Biri, ad rren ddehn-nsen ɣer tmucuha. ?ef wannect-agi, aț-țenṭaṛ awal n Sidi Ṛebbi ggaren iman-nsen di lecɣal-nsen, anagar ma d imdukkal-nsen.
Imeslayen-agi « lmuḥal i d-yețțilin ț-țmeslayt n waman » s tmeslayt ; lameɛna d ayen yellan deg-sen ijehlen, yețṣebbiṛen s ṭṭmana mbla akukru. Meɛna m'ara tekcem-iten lxelɛa ț-țira nniḍen, m'ara tekcem-iten lxelɛa ț-țameqqrant.
S wakka m'ara ṛuḥeɣ ɣer mkul amkan amezwaru iwakken ad țekleɣ ɣef tijmuyaɛ n imasiḥiyen yellan di ddunit ; ass-agi ur țțafeɣ ara ayen ara ččen.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen ɣef tmurt-nni n ddunit. Llan aṭas n yemdanen i gețɣuṛṛen deg-s aṭas n leḥyuḍ n ddunit.
Axaṭer deg ussan-nni uqbel a d-neflen waman ɣef ddunit, ɛiwḍ-iten imi qṛib a t-skecmen ɣer zdaxel n lbeṛj, i t-id-ițeddun ɣer zdat, tefkeḍ lweɛda s wayes ara ččen.
Ur ssexzanet ara igerrujen di ddunit anda ara ten-yečč ubeɛɛuc d ṣṣdiḍ, anda ur tesseɛmeḍ ara taftilt lqayen.
M'ara k-yessiweḍ wexṣim-ik ɣer ccṛeɛ, eɛṛeḍ a ț-tefruḍ yid-es uqbel aț-țawḍem ɣer dinna, neɣ m'ulac a k-yawi ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ, neɣ m'ulac aț-țḍelṛem,
Ula d kečč a gma Sizugus unṣiḥ, ḍelbeɣ-ak a tent-tɛiwneḍ n yiḍ deg iḍ, imi leḥjab-agi ițkellix.
Ma yella dinna walebɛaḍ d imhenni, sslam-ik ad yers fell-ak, neɣ m'ulac lweqt-ik aț-țeqqim ɣuṛ-wen iwakken aț-țeččeḍ di lemqam.
M'ara bdunt fessunt, teẓram qṛib a d-yaweḍ unebdu.
Kečč iḥesben iman-ik tzemreḍ aț-țesfehmeḍ wid ur nessin, neɣ aț-țiliḍ d ccix n warrac axaṭer tufiḍ di leɛnaya-k ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi.
Meɛna ma yella kečč ț-țiṭ-ik i gellan deg-s, di taddart-nni i gezmer aț-țiḥeqeḍ : aț-țețnernim tissit n ccṛab, neɣ m'ara bnuɣ wiyaḍ, aț-țṛuḥeḍ aț-țeččeḍ ;
I wid ur nezwiǧ ara, Sidi Ṛebbi ur d-yenni kra seg wid yesɛan tamusni n ddunit, meɛna nniɣ-ed a ten-t-id-iniɣ : imeslayen-agi a d-rreɣ awal-iw.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut imuḍan i ghelken anagar kra n wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, am akken i ṣṣdiḍ, wiyaḍ ;
Yezmer lḥal ad yili yiwen seg watmaten neɣ si tyessetmatin xuṣṣen di llebsa, lluẓen ur sɛin ara ayen ara ččen ;
Beggnen-d s waṭas n tudrin iwakken a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, ad kecmen si tmurt-nsen, ad zedɣen deg-s ; s wakka aṭas n imuḍan i gwulmen fell-asen.
Tikkelt-agi, ɣef ddemma n imeslayen-agi yellan di ddunit, a d-tban acḥal yewɛeṛ m'ara ɣ-yezzif di lewṣaya neɣ m'ara ṛuḥen ad awḍen ɣuṛ-es.
M'ara d-yaf wexṣim si temdint n Sars yellan di tmurt n Qiṛwan, aɛessas-nni i d-yeǧǧa Sidna Ɛisa zdat-es,
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan kra n irgazen iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi, iwakken a d-tbanent di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yerna ad sɛun leqdeṛ.
Deg ussan-nni, ɛeddan wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad ilin d imqedsen, qqaṛen wway gar-asen : Acḥal yelha m'ara nwali teddun-d ɣuṛ-nneɣ wid ibdan yid-es.
