Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ ilaq a d-yedṛu wayagi meṛṛa ?
Lejdud-agi ț-țamajt n tmes i d yusan si tmurt n Yahuda armi ț-țamurt n tmes i d-ițfeggiḍen seg iṛeqqen.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla akukru, ma d lecɣal-nsen alamma ț-țameddit, qṛib a d-yeɣli ṭṭlam ɣef rrif n lebḥeṛ n mkul tutlayt.
Ad ilin azal n meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin alef n yemdanen i gellan dinna yiwen ufellaḥ i gzedɣen dinna, ɣeṛqen aṭas n wid akk yumnen s Lmasiḥ.
Tekker yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu iǧehden, agummaḍ i lebḥeṛ wwin si lebḥeṛ ɣer lebḥeṛ,
