Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s yiwet n tiṭ wala aț-țesɛuḍ snat wallen, aț- țwaḍeggṛeḍ ɣer tewwurt.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wid ițbeddilen idrimen akk-d wid yeznuzun.
Ɣas akken ṛṛusul nnan asen azal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen, meɛna ula d yiwen seg-sen mmuten.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant iger iman-is ur nesɛi azal, ur t-tewqiɛ ara lmeɛna, axaṭer akken yura di tira iqedsen : Tawṛat n lweqt-agi, qṛib a s-kksen abrid icebḥen.
Imiren kan, ț-țagi i d lmuḥal aya n leḥjab yellan di tegzirt-agi. Mi tella amkan-nni anda tella tezmert, acḥal lqay, acḥal ɛlay leḥmala n diri i gețmeslay.
lameɛna si terbaɛt n temdint n Ludikus a sen-yefk tijmaɛin, iskker-iten zdat ines kan taɛekkumt ẓẓayen, yesɛan azal n t lehḍurt.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lmut.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d laẓ ;
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen.
Meɛna imdanen-agi țɛicin am lmal n lexla, lhan kan i ṣṣyada, ur țxemmimen ara, reggmen ayen akken yella di lɛaddat n idurar iwakken ad ḥebsent lexsaṛa, am akken d llebsa-nsen.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim, acerrig-nni ad innerni.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Ilaq yal yiwen deg-wen ad inadi ɣef nnfeɛ n wiyaḍ iwakken ad nnernin di liman.
